Created Dashboard using 3 worksheets.

Right click on New worksheet then click New Dashboard. 


Now we can click Floating. 


Now drag and drop % of Total Hourly Wages for each Hire Date sheets on the worksheet. 


Drag and drop Taxes of Each Category sheets on the worksheet


Now drag and drop Total Employee Of Each Region sheets on the worksheet. 



Click More Options then click Title. 



See % of Total Hourly Wages for each Hire Date title is not on the sheet. Same way we can delete other Title. 


Click on Filter, then Action will happen. 


Click on South Region Filter, see other two filter showing South Region


Right click on sheet name then click Rename. And write sheet name. 



Click on Dashboard then click Show Title 


Dashboard Title Employee Region 



Picture showing only South Region, Taxes of Each Category worksheet

Picture showing only South Region, Total Employee of Each Region worksheet. 

Dashboard Employee Region.
